ZH: 我们要献出爱心，帮助需要帮助的人。
EN: We should offer our love to help those in need.

ZH: 我们应该献身于科学事业。
EN: We should dedicate ourselves to the field of science.

ZH: 他献出了自己的生命，保护了国家。
EN: He sacrificed his life to protect the country.

ZH: 这本书是他献给我的生日礼物。
EN: This book is a birthday gift he gave me.

ZH: 这些画作都是他献给博物馆的作品。
EN: These paintings are all works he donated to the museum.

ZH: 她献出了一切，想要拯救这个世界。
EN: She gave up everything to save the world.

ZH: 他献上了他的一生，为了追求艺术的完美。
EN: He devoted his whole life to pursue perfection in art.

ZH: 他献出了所有金钱，帮助了许多贫困家庭。
EN: He donated all his money to help many impoverished families.

ZH: 我们应该献上我们的心意，向他表达感谢之情。
EN: We should offer our gratitude to him.

ZH: 她献了一个惊喜的吻，把他感动地落泪了。
EN: She gave him a surprising kiss that brought tears to his eyes.

ZH: 我要献给你这首歌，希望你喜欢。
EN: I'll dedicate this song to you, I hope you like it.

ZH: 这幅画是我专门献给你的。
EN: This painting is specially dedicated to you.

ZH: 我献上我的祝福，祝你生日快乐。
EN: I offer you my blessings and wish you a happy birthday.

ZH: 他献了一支花，放在了她的墓前。
EN: He laid a flower at her grave as a tribute.

ZH: 她献出了自己的音乐才华，给了这首曲子生命。
EN: She poured her musical talent into this piece, giving it life.

